snippet.title: Titenic (NES) Longplay [241]
snippet.description: Based on factual events, this whole disaster happened just the way the game tells us. Regarding the game, it was played for the first time by me and the enemies and mechanics are very awkward and wonky to deal with, especially the last boss fight.
